<section class="section-sm">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
        <div class="content">
          
          <h3 id="information-collection">Information We Collect</h3>
          <p>At Fin-Dinari, we collect certain identifying personal data when you sign up to our Service including your name, email address, phone number, and financial information necessary to provide our budgeting, investment, and community features. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring your financial data remains secure.</p>
          
          <h3 id="data-protection">Data Protection & Security</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Encrypted Storage:</strong> All your financial data is encrypted using industry-standard encryption protocols.</li>
            <li><strong>No Data Sharing:</strong> We never sell your personal or financial information to third parties.</li>
            <li><strong>Your Control:</strong> You have complete control over what information you share with the community.</li>
            <li><strong>Anonymous Mode:</strong> Participate in community discussions without revealing your identity.</li>
            <li><strong>Private Messaging:</strong> All direct messages are encrypted and private.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 id="information-usage">How We Use Your Information</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>To provide personalized financial insights and AI-powered recommendations</li>
            <li>To track your expenses, investments, and progress toward financial goals</li>
            <li>To enable community features like groups, mentorship, and challenges</li>
            <li>To send important notifications about your account and financial alerts</li>
            <li>To improve our services and develop new features based on user feedback</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 id="community-privacy">Community & Privacy Controls</h3>
          <p>Fin-Dinari's community features are designed with privacy in mind. You can choose exactly what to share with the community - from your financial wins and goals to your investment portfolio performance. Our platform includes:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Granular Privacy Settings:</strong> Control who sees your posts, goals, and investment activity</li>
            <li><strong>Moderated Community:</strong> All content is moderated to prevent spam, harassment, and negativity</li>
            <li><strong>Block & Report Features:</strong> You have full control over who can interact with you</li>
            <li><strong>Anonymous Participation:</strong> Join discussions without revealing your identity or financial status</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 id="third-party-services">Third-Party Services</h3>
          <p>Fin-Dinari integrates with trusted financial institutions and payment processors solely to provide our core services. We never share more information than necessary, and all third-party partners are bound by strict data protection agreements. You can disconnect any integrated service at any time.</p>
          
          <h3 id="your-rights">Your Rights</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of all personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update or correct any inaccurate information</li>
            <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your account and all associated data</li>
            <li><strong>Export:</strong> Download all your financial data in CSV/PDF/Excel format</li>
            <li><strong>Opt-Out:</strong> Unsubscribe from marketing communications at any time</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 id="data-retention">Data Retention</h3>
          <p>We retain your personal and financial data for as long as your account is active. If you close your account, we will delete all your personal information within 30 days, unless we are required to retain certain data for legal or regulatory compliance. Anonymous, aggregated data may be retained for analytical purposes.</p>
          
          <h3 id="children-privacy">Children's Privacy</h3>
          <p>Fin-Dinari is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we learn that we have collected personal information from a child under 13, we will delete that information immediately.</p>
          
          <h3 id="policy-updates">Updates to This Policy</h3>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.</p>
          
          <h3 id="contact-us">Contact Us</h3>
          <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> privacy@findinari.com</li>
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +216 12 345 678</li>
            <li><strong>Address:</strong> Technopole El Ghazala, Ariana, 2083, Tunisia</li>
          </ul>
          
          <p class="mt-5"><em>Last Updated: April 2026</em></p>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

